。 内容来源英媒记者走进关税战下的义乌：多数已做好准备，将重心转向美国以外市场_中国_特朗普本_贸易"},"attached_info":"CkoI7K2HiZTRuIV+EAMaCTExNDQyMDgxOCCn1ty/BjAAOOACQBhyEzE4OTM2MDk1MDM1NTcxNDkxNzJ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"50 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-06e5e0b42004dec7119e55d4c616351b_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"25_1744548316.841879","card_id":"Q_1894388873636840866","target":{"id":1894388873636841000,"title":"赛飞儿触碰遐蝶时为何没有死亡？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/1894388873636840866","type":"question","created":1744437503,"answer_count":31,"follower_count":45,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[781978,3878712,3934443],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"如同传送开拓者那样，赛飞儿在传送遐蝶时一定会触碰到她，为什么不会死亡？"},"attached_info":"CkkI7K2HiZTRuIV+EAMaCTExNDQ1ODY2MiD/gei/BjAAOC1AGXITMTg5NDM4ODg3MzYzNjg0MDg2NngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"49 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-53b9c5a37f3fb7be2a56de7f5501d2a0_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"26_1744548316.842274","card_id":"Q_15751298897","target":{"id":15751298897,"title":"春天你所在的城市有哪些常见的开花植物？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/15751298897","type":"question","created":1742973581,"answer_count":194,"follower_count":218,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1540,3381,12217,15455,3904557],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"4月10日-4月30日，参与活动，赢春日好礼！春日滞留计划"},"attached_info":"CkII7K2HiZTRuIV+EAMaCTExNDE4MjQxNSCN1Y6/BjAAONoBQBpyCzE1NzUxMjk4ODk3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"49 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"